Configure SageMaker User Profiles: Create SageMaker user profiles for each user (nilesh.tondale@amexgbt.com, chandan@amexgbt.com, vivek@amexgbt.com). Associate each user profile with the MLOPSAgemkaer IAM role.

User Access: When users log in to SageMaker using their email IDs, SageMaker will authenticate them and assume the MLOPSAgemkaer IAM role associated with their user profile. The IAM policies attached to that IAM role will determine the users' access to S3 resources based on their email IDs.
